name: VR Anatomy (VirtuBod)
summary: Comprehensive Human Anatomy package combines immersive and detailed reproductions of the human body. Designed by leading experts in the field, the individual topics provide accurate and detailed representations of various parts and systems within the human body. The content supports learners studying anatomy, medicine, DO, nursing, occupational therapy, physical therapy, and beyond by delivering a captivating sensory and visual experience contributing to a deeper understanding of human anatomy.
